        <div class="expand row-fluid content" role="main">
        	<div class="span12">
            <p>The page you are looking for is not here. It may have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
      <h2>Please try the following:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>If you typed the URL in the Address bar, make sure that it is spelled correctly.</li>
        <li>Go back to <a href="/" title="UBC homepage">our homepage</a> and browse for the information you need.</li>
        <li>Try searching for it using our <a href="/search/" title="Search">search</a> page.</li>
        <li>The <a href="/landing/atoz.html" title="A-Z websites">A-Z websites listing</a> provides an overview of all UBC websites.</li>
        <li>Click the Back button to try another link.</li>
      </ul>
             </div>
        </div>
        
